trans-unit.source: Supports the page parser in defining the behavior for how content is parsed.
trans-unit.target: 支援頁面剖析器定義內容的剖析行為。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The object to use to parse files.
trans-unit.target: 要用來剖析檔案的物件。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> class with the specified template parser.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的樣板剖析器，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the objects to persist that were built by the root builder.
trans-unit.target: 取得根產生器所建置要保存之物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Hashtable" /> object that contains the objects that were built by the root builder.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Hashtable" /> 物件，包含根產生器所建置的物件。

trans-unit.source: The tag name of the child control.
The <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> object that holds all the specified tag attributes.
trans-unit.target: 包含所有指定標記屬性的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns the control type of any parsed child controls.
trans-unit.target: 傳回任何已剖析子控制項的控制項型別。

trans-unit.source: The type of the child control.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method overrides the implementation of this method in <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A>方法的實作中，這個方法會覆寫<xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>。

trans-unit.source: Provides a way to modify the <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit" /> object after code generation is finished.
trans-unit.target: 提供可在完成程式碼產生作業後修改 <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit" /> 物件的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder.OnCodeGenerationComplete%2A> method is called when the CodeDom tree has been fully built.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.RootBuilder.OnCodeGenerationComplete%2A>完全內建的 CodeDom 樹狀目錄時，呼叫方法。
